OL,5, Pressure is growing on BBC chairman    
OL,6, Richard Sharp after a critical report  
OL,7, from MPs into his appointment.         
OL,9,FHe made "significant errors of         
OL,10,Fjudgement" acting as a go-between on a 
OL,11,Floan for Boris Johnson, while applying 
OL,12,Ffor the post, the committee said.      
OL,14,FThe SNP's John Nicolson, a committee   
OL,15,Fmember, told the BBC Mr Sharp's        
OL,16,Fposition was "extremely difficult".    
OL,18,FMr Sharp said he did not help arrange a
OL,19,Fguarantee on the loan or give Mr       
OL,20,FJohnson financial advice.              
